{
  "stem": "27390.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Otherwise, the person, every person will be x-rayed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And if they found-- because we couldn't have anything on us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It's only what was in the body, because-- we were told to undress.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Anyway, so the people that came forward, they, they, we heard them taken out-- we, we, we saw them being taken out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And in the dark we couldn't see very much because if they took away the torch it was dark.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they kept coming back and taking people out, and we heard shots, and shots, and shots to frighten us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The people should hand over the valuables.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "This went on all night like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "In the morning, we were pushed off into the-- in front of every barrack was such a space where we-- we stood for appell.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "In the morning it was bitter cold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We only had the-- I'm mixing it up a bit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We were taken into a place before, and we were told to undress.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we were given these pajamas with a cap, a striped cap to put on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And from there we were taken out and taken into this place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And in the morning we, we, we were-- and in all this time we didn't get anything to eat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So in, in, about lunchtime that day-- in the morning was very cold.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "In the daytime it was turning very hot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So they started distributing some soup.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So whoever queued up for the soup got such a beating that the bowl of soup was more on the floor than they managed to get to eat.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Anyway, then we were picked out three-- 800 boys from all the grown-ups, all the adults.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They separated 800 boys into a separate barrack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And in this barrack we were for about three days.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
